data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Price Improvement! Seize the opportunity to live your dream in this exceptional single-family home, with its unbeatable location, ample size, and outstanding affordability.  "Sarasota named 50 Best Places to Live" from Money Magazine.  This versatile home is ideal for new owners who are a growing family or multigenerational or desire a relocation oasis in the highly desired city of North Port Florida.  The split open floor plan and the benefit of a large study/den give options for a home office, media room, or a fourth bedroom with minor changes.     The kitchen size is ideal for gatherings showcasing granite counters.  The open plan allows easy access to the dining and spacious living areas. Enjoy the stainless appliances for timeless pleasure.  The large master suite gives ample space with an en-suite bathroom with granite tops marble-tiled shower, along a walk-in closet. Enjoy the updated floors in the living, den, and master suite, and new carpet in the guest bedrooms.  The laundry room is located inside for safety and convenience.     Ideal location and no flood zone provide access to regional airports, world-class fishing, boating, beaches, and golf.  North Port is recognized as a fast-growing city with healthcare, sporting venues, world-class Warm Mineral Springs, and two major league spring training parks  This is a family-focused community giving long-term opportunities to raise a family or enjoy the easy life of Florida. The roof was replaced in 2020.
